  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Three-Arm, Phase IIIb Study Comparing the Safety and Efficacy of Interferon Gamma-1b Alone, IFN-Gamma 1b With Azathioprine, and Azathioprine Alone in Patients With Idiopathic Pulmonary Fibrosis Receiving Prednisone</official_title>
